description:
Clients in Yakima, Washington, and throughout the Tri-County area often require an experienced attorney when faced with bankruptcy and other financial struggles. At Olsen Daines Bankruptcy Attorneys, our law offices focus on client satisfaction. We offer free initial consultations where we listen carefully to the details of each case. From there, we explore all potential legal options and choose the route that best meets the needs of our valued clients. Our attorneys, who are admitted to practice before the State Courts and United States District Courts for Eastern and Western Districts of Washington and Oregon, have a thorough knowledge of state and federal laws and regulations.

Our law offices have over 30 years of experience handling a wide range of bankruptcy issues, including creditor harassment, vehicle repossession, back child support, foreclosure, wage garnishments, license suspension and discharged taxes. We understand the emotions that may be tied to these matters and are compassionate when assisting clients through the process, every step of the way.

In addition to bankruptcies, the law offices of Olsen Daines Bankruptcy Attorneys assist people throughout Oregon with their personal injury cases. From truck collisions, motorcycle accidents and motor vehicle accidents to birth injuries, traumatic brain damage and wrongful death, we partner with clients to build a solid case. We also accept credit cards as well as other forms of payment for our services.

We are a debt relief agency. We help people file for bankruptcy relief under the U.S. Bankruptcy Code.
